{save true}{false}ifelse}{false}ifelse
11 dict begin
/FontType 1 def
/FontMatrix [0.001 0 0 0.001 0 0 ]readonly def
/FontName /WBFWDY+CMR10 def
/FontBBox {-40 -250 1009 750 }readonly def
/PaintType 0 def
